# Manifest Compliance (Firefox/AMO)

- Add Firefox data consent keys under `browser_specific_settings.gecko` (validate with AMO linter):
```json
{
  "browser_specific_settings": {
    "gecko": {
      "strict_min_version": "109.0",
      "data_collection_permissions": {
        "required": []
      }
    }
  }
}
```
- Keep permissions minimal and host-specific.
- Ensure `content_scripts.matches` aligns with providers; keep CDN hosts only if needed for images.

